Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: El Salvador crisis
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043wzvq
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 1 May 1983
Fears of Soviet aid for opposition prompt US to consider assisting El Salvador's embattled government. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less